text: Karaozek () is a rural locality (a selo) in Vatazhensky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 552 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 61 km from Astrakhan, 23 km from Krasny Yar, on the Kazakhstan–Russia border. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Karaozek
